sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant A as Databricks App<br/>(OpenAI Agents SDK)
    participant FM as Foundation Model<br/>(Claude via AI Gateway)
    participant LB as Lakebase<br/>(Postgres · agent_openai_memory)

    U->>A: First message (no session_id yet)
    Note over A: get_session_id(): none found,<br/>so generate a new UUID
    A->>LB: open session · get_items(session_id)
    LB-->>A: empty — brand-new thread
    Note over A: deduplicate_input: no history,<br/>send full input = [ first message ]
    A->>FM: system prompt + tools + [ first message ]
    FM-->>A: assistant reply
    A->>LB: add_items([ user msg, assistant msg ])
    Note over LB: INSERT rows keyed by session_id
    A-->>U: reply + session_id (custom_outputs)
    Note over U,LB: Client keeps the session_id to continue this thread later
